"""Test get_cache_partition_perf_stats."""
response = self.perf.get_cache_partition_perf_stats(cache_partition_id=self
    .p_data.cache_part_id, metrics=pc.KPI, start_time=self.time_now,
    end_time=self.time_now)
self.assertIsInstance(response, dict)
self.assertEqual(response.get('reporting_level'), self.common.
    convert_to_snake_case(pc.CACHE_PART))
